<h3>Selected parts of cookie</h3>

<ul>
    <li>Base: {{cookie.base}} - {{pricify (findPrice bases cookie.base)}} PLN.</li>
    {{#each cookie.addons}}
        <li>Addon: {{this}} - {{pricify (findPrice  @root.aadons this)}} PLN. <a href="/configurator/delete-addon/{{this}}">Delete</a> </li>
    {{/each}}
</ul>
<p>
    <strong>Total of {{pricify sum}} PLN</strong>
</p>